headline: Xcel Energy Stock Powers Ahead With A Bright Future
summary: Investors searching for a stock with strong long-term growth potential and solid dividend growth might be content with Xcel Energy (XEL). Xcel, headquartered in Minneapolis, Minn., sells electricity to 3.9 million customers and natural gas to 2.2 million customers across eight states.
